{"comments":"Z-Index atoms — stacking order in the z-axis.\n\n## CSS Stacking Context\n\nZ-index only has meaning within a stacking context. Elements with\n`position: static` (the default) do not participate in z-index ordering.\n\nA new stacking context is created by:\n- `position: relative/absolute/fixed/sticky` with `z-index` other than `auto`\n- `opacity` less than 1\n- `transform`, `filter`, `perspective`, etc.\n- `isolation: isolate`\n\n## Value Range\n\nCSS z-index accepts any integer. In practice:\n- Browsers clamp to approximately ±2147483647 (32-bit signed int)\n- Values beyond ±9999 are rarely needed\n- Negative values place elements behind the default layer\n\n## Concrete Values\n\nThis module provides a typed wrapper around integers. BrandSchema can\ndefine semantic z-index scales (e.g., `modal`, `dropdown`, `tooltip`)\nby assigning concrete ZIndex values.\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Schema.Elevation.ZIndex as ZIndex\n\n-- Create z-index values\ndropdownZ :: ZIndex.ZIndex\ndropdownZ = ZIndex.z 100\n\n-- Auto (default stacking)\ndefaultZ :: ZIndex.ZIndex\ndefaultZ = ZIndex.auto\n\n-- Convert to CSS\ncss = ZIndex.toLegacyCss dropdownZ  -- \"100\"\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[103,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/ZIndex.purs","start":[103,3]},"title":"ZIndexAuto"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[104,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/ZIndex.purs","start":[104,3]},"title":"ZIndexValue"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Elevation","ZIndex"],"ZIndex"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[106,38],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/ZIndex.purs","start":[106,1]},"title":"eqZIndex"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Elevation","ZIndex"],"ZIndex"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[127,56],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/ZIndex.purs","start":[123,1]},"title":"ordZIndex"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Elevation","ZIndex"],"ZIndex"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[130,21],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/ZIndex.purs","start":[129,1]},"title":"showZIndex"}],"comments":"Z-index value for CSS stacking order\n\nEither a concrete integer or `auto` (browser default).\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"data","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[104,20],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/ZIndex.purs","start":[102,1]},"title":"ZIndex"},{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[118,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/ZIndex.purs","start":[118,3]},"title":"Isolate"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[119,18],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/ZIndex.purs","start":[119,3]},"title":"IsolationAuto"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Elevation","ZIndex"],"IsolationMode"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[121,52],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/ZIndex.purs","start":[121,1]},"title":"eqIsolationMode"}],"comments":"Isolation mode for stacking context creation.\n\nCSS `isolation` property controls whether an element creates a new\nstacking context. This is useful for containing z-index values\nwithin a subtree.\n\n- `isolate`: Creates a new stacking context (like z-index: 0 but\n  without requiring position: relative)\n- `auto`: Inherits stacking context from parent (default)\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"data","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[119,18],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/ZIndex.purs","start":[117,1]},"title":"IsolationMode"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create a z-index from an integer\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Elevation","ZIndex"],"ZIndex"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[137,19],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/ZIndex.purs","start":[137,1]},"title":"z"},{"children":[],"comments":"Auto z-index (default browser stacking)\n\nElement participates in normal document flow stacking.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Elevation","ZIndex"],"ZIndex"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[143,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/ZIndex.purs","start":[143,1]},"title":"auto"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create a negative z-index\n\nPlaces element behind the default stacking layer.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotat